data.title: AniPlaylist
data.meta_description: AniPlaylist helps you find your favorite original anime openings, endings, OST on Spotify & Apple Music.
data.text:
Browser Compatibility

AniPlaylist.com is not compatible with Internet Explorer. We recommend you to use Chrome, Firefox, Safari or Edge.

Found a missing song or album? Feel free to submit it!
